  <name>Bluetooth Bitrate Manager</name>
  <summary>Monitor and manage PipeWire Bluetooth audio codecs</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Bluetooth Bitrate Manager is a GTK4 application that monitors and manages
      PipeWire Bluetooth audio codecs with real-time bitrate information.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Monitor active Bluetooth audio codec and bitrate in real-time</li>
      <li>Support for SBC, AAC, aptX, LDAC, and LC3 codecs</li>
      <li>Optional high-bitpool SBC rebuild for improved audio quality</li>
      <li>Command-line interface for scripting and automation</li>
      <li>Modern GTK4 and libadwaita interface</li>
      <li>Seamless PipeWire integration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

